data.description: Discover the epitome of luxury living in this captivating 4-bedroom, 3-bath, 3764 sqft home nestled on a sprawling 5-acre estate, showcasing exquisite European-style architecture. Immerse yourself in the fine craftsmanship and attention to detail that defines this custom residence.    Step inside to be greeted by the allure of beautiful hardwood floors, complemented by 9+ foot high ceilings adorned with crown molding, creating an atmosphere of elegance throughout. The heart of this home is the stunning remodeled kitchen, boasting a center island, breakfast bar, ample cabinetry with granite countertops, and a charming eat-in area featuring a corner fireplace.    The expansive great room is a true focal point, highlighting a large masonry fireplace and a wall of windows, with French doors that seamlessly open to a courtyard offering breathtaking views of meticulously landscaped gardens and a tree-lined yard.    The master bedroom suite on the main level is a sanctuary of comfort, featuring state-of-the-art shower facilities, a luxurious jetted tub, and an additional guest bedroom for added convenience. Upstairs, a teen suite awaits, providing extra space for privacy or leisure.    With a 3-car garage and a versatile barn/workshop, this property is not only a dream home but also a functional and well-equipped space for your lifestyle needs. Don't miss the opportunity to own a piece of paradise where sophistication meets comfort, and every detail reflects the pinnacle of quality living. Your extraordinary home awaits!          NOTE: Principals of the seller may share ownership in a licensed real estate brokerage.
